#originalTopic=does-owning-a-gun-make-you-safer
Reasons   gun control   doesn't work:1. Criminals by definition break   the law  . 2. Criminals get   guns   from family or friends, not   gun shows   or gun stores.3. Preventing   law  -abiding citizens from attaining guns will only help criminals by keeping guns away from law-abiding citizens.